    div(class = "well").bcGradient
        div().container.text-center
            div.container
                div().row.center
                    div.col-md-4
                    div.col-md-4.bcBanner
            div.container.text-center
                div.row
                    div(class = "guildProgression").col-md-12.text-center
                        | At this time it is not possible to determine raid progression using the blizzard api.




